# ⚠️ Wrong Package!

You probably meant to install **praisonai-svc** (singular, not plural).

This is a defensive package to prevent typosquatting.
The correct package will be installed automatically.

## Correct Installation:

```bash
pip install praisonai-svc
```

## Why this package exists

This package exists to protect users from accidentally installing a typosquatted package.
If you installed this by mistake, the correct package (`praisonai-svc`) has been installed as a dependency.

## Official Package

- **Correct name:** `praisonai-svc`
- **Repository:** https://github.com/MervinPraison/PraisonAI-SVC
- **Documentation:** https://mervinpraison.github.io/PraisonAI-SVC

## Report Issues

If you believe this is a security issue, please report it:
- GitHub: https://github.com/MervinPraison/PraisonAI-SVC/issues
